Subject:Brides waiting for you
I do not know what to start with that’s why I will start with the description of my character. 
I consider myself quite a knowledgeable and clever girl, also I am  very beautiful and generous. 

I always try to keep myself in a good shape.. It seems to be foolish to describe imaginary image of a loved one. 

I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my special one. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is far from being very important. The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be positive, educated and very attentive. I want to love and to be loved http://colaremo.yaraho.com Let's begin our acquaintance 


